{"type": "article", "id": 24461, "title": "这 12 个建筑事务所设计的户外猫窝，会有什么不同？", "description": "这些户外猫窝都是为流浪猫准备的。", "date": "2016-03-25T11:14:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 16841, "name": "猫窝"}, {"id": 25397, "name": "流浪猫救助"}, {"id": 3313, "name": "洛杉矶"}, {"id": 25398, "name": "FixNation"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 224, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021136150hx7eM4mJzE1kyST.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p><a href=\"http://fixnation.org/\">FixNation</a> 是一个洛杉矶公益机构，它是由一对夫妇——Mark Dodge 和 Karn Myers 共同创立的。自 1999 年 10 月份起，这对夫妇便开始救助流浪猫，2007 年，他们成立的 FixNation 成为洛杉矶第一个全职救助流浪猫的机构，他们提供整套救助、治疗、领养的服务，迄今为止已救助超过 18000 只流浪猫。</p>\n<p>最近，他们发起了一个叫作<a href=\"http://fixnation.org/2016/03/and-the-architects-for-animals-fan-favorite-is/\">“给猫建庇护所”（Architects for Animals “Giving Shelter”）</a>的活动，邀请建筑师为流浪猫设计户外庇护所。共有 12 个建筑事务所参加了这个活动，他们为猫猫们设计了形态各异的小家。其中， Abramson Teiger Architects 设计的 “The Cat Bowl” 被该机构评选为“最受欢迎小窝”。我们来看看所有的设计作品吧：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113607c38aJRNM2k9Dbovu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第一个作品：Abramson Teiger Architects 设计的，名为 The Cat Bowl ，在此次活动中，它也被人们评选为“最喜爱的猫窝”</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113607lVxn1WsTvoB8RZ4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第二个作品： CallisonRTKL 设计的猫窝，非常有建筑感</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113608TGn1KASQxkYcaHoz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.08625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第三个作品： DSH 设计的猫窝。如果把这个窝放在户外，也太不稳固了啊</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113608ngW7VwUJZ1yLolGk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第四个作品：这是三家机构合作设计的， Formation Association、 Arktura 和 BuroHappold。它模仿的是自然岩石</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113609Ec2rUvgX3do8siJp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.945\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第五个作品：HOK 设计的猫窝，比较中规中矩</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021136095rMuVBU0aAzIFlWC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第六个作品：Knowhow Shop 设计的猫窝，下雨时猫猫可以躲藏在其中</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113609JTmHhGE8ftoCdcBr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第七个作品：Lehrer Architects 设计的窝，抽象</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021136104YGfVkBAjnM87yuE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第八个作品：是  Perkins &amp; Will 设计的，四居室啊</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113611NhF9XjvScLMOJ1Vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第九个作品：Pfeiffer Partners Architects 设计的</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113611ZABCYw5yIvzXpS0J.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第十个作品：RNL 设计的</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113612xRehNi629vYVPyG7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5825\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第十一个作品：由  Standard Architecture|Design 设计，不知道猫猫趴在里面能否舒服？</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021136121JhfLkmPoxVlztKr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">第十二个作品：WORD 和 Schmidt Designs 共同设计的</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">除了这次参赛作品，我们还搜集到了许多其他的猫窝，一起来看看吧。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113612Mw1G7AiNdu3vCS86.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Space Intl 设计的猫窝，人猫共处</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113613ULbTWHx7XGeDZRJI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96339114\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Standard Architecture Design 设计的猫窝</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113613pz2hVOYvBrI53PWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7788162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Abramson Teiger Architects 设计的猫窝</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021136143hbsq2d1GiyQHMp9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97465887\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">DHS Architecture 设计的猫窝</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702113614BHDctrgSebF2s7Xk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.27226463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">HOK 的猫窝作品</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://fixnation.org/2016/03/and-the-architects-for-animals-fan-favorite-is/\">fixnation</a></p>\n\n"}